                <head/>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The editors welcome the turn of events in Maryland where Governor Swann
                    appears ready to triumph in his conflict with the Baltimore Commissioners of
                    Election.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
